    "No Gradients on Text: Keep text solid for readability.",
    "Interactive Elements: All buttons/links must have hover/active states.",
    "Data-TestID: Add data-testid to all interactive elements.",
    "Spacing: Use generous padding (py-20, py-24) for sections.",
    "Borders: Use subtle borders (border-border) instead of heavy shadows."
