  "instructions_to_main_agent": "1. Install 'lucide-react', 'framer-motion', 'clsx', 'tailwind-merge'. 2. Update tailwind.config.js with the colors and fonts. 3. Create a 'Layout' component that handles the Navbar and Footer. 4. Implement the Theme Toggle immediately. 5. Use the provided image URLs strictly. 6. Build the 'Home' page first with the Hero, Stats, and Courses sections."
